        "Nj\u00eb gjykat\u00ebs \u00ebsht\u00eb q\u00eblluar p\u00ebr vdekje dhe dy polic\u00eb jan\u00eb plagosur n\u00eb incidente t\u00eb ndara n\u00eb Dagestan. Autoritetet b\u00ebn\u00eb t\u00eb ditur se trupi i Magomed Khasbulatovit u gjet n\u00eb makin\u00ebn e tij.\nMilitant\u00ebt islamist\u00eb n\u00eb Kaukazin Verior po luftojn\u00eb forcat ruse me vite, me q\u00ebllim t\u00eb themelimit t\u00eb nj\u00eb shteti t\u00eb pavarur islamik.",
        "Nga Basir \u00c7ollaku\nKLP-ja p\u00ebrzgjodhi 15 prokuror\u00eb me prioritet p\u00ebr t\u00eb qen\u00eb b\u00ebrthama e par\u00eb e SPAK, ndon\u00ebse pik\u00ebzimi \u00ebsht\u00eb nj\u00eb novel\u00eb m\u00eb vete p\u00ebr nga m\u00ebnyra e fasoneris\u00eb se si ka funksionuar. T\u00eb mbeturit n\u00eb zgrip ose jasht\u00eb 15-shes do t\u00eb jen\u00eb s\u00ebrish me vendime KLP prokuror\u00eb t\u00eb thjesht\u00eb n\u00ebp\u00ebr rrethe, atje ku e meritojn\u00eb sipas m\u00ebkatit.\nT\u00eb mbetur n\u00eb periferi ishin k\u00ebt\u00eb her\u00eb Besim Hajdarmataj, Donika Prela, Dritan Pren\u00e7i e Vladimir Mara. Duke l\u00ebn\u00eb m\u00ebnjan\u00eb Donika Prel\u00ebn tre prokuro\u00ebt e tjer\u00eb, megjith\u00eb ng\u00ebr\u00e7et kan\u00eb pasur dosjet m\u00eb t\u00eb r\u00ebnda me pesh\u00eb politike. Tahirin, 339, dhe kan\u00eb firmosur jo pak. K\u00ebta nuk jan\u00eb sepse mundeshin. T\u00eb tjer\u00eb m\u00eb shum\u00eb se gjysma e atyre q\u00eb jan\u00eb n\u00eb rradhe nuk kan\u00eb firmosur asgj\u00eb dhe mos kini shpres\u00eb se do t\u00eb b\u00ebjn\u00eb ndonj\u00eb gj\u00eb. Sepse jan\u00eb borxhlinj. Jo thjesht nga vetting, se m\u00eb vet\u00eb mundeshin edhe t\u00eb kalonin. Por sepse kan\u00eb hyr\u00eb n\u00eb borxhe t\u00eb reja. Kan\u00eb fshehur ose jan\u00eb dakord\u00ebsuar p\u00ebr ndonj\u00eb hall dhe tani jan\u00eb gati t\u00eb kthejn\u00eb kusuret.\nFesta p\u00ebr SPAK \u00ebsht\u00eb nj\u00eb hibrid diplomatik dhe muzikor, sepse duhej s\u00eb paku t\u00eb kishte n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb dit\u00eb nga donator\u00ebt e m\u00ebdhenj nd\u00ebrkomb\u00ebtar\u00eb, emra t\u00eb politikan\u00ebve t\u00eb arrestuar, ku nd\u00ebrkomb\u00ebtar\u00ebt na lajm\u00ebruan fort her\u00eb se do ndodh\u00eb patjet\u00ebr.\nSepse po ju kujtoj nj\u00eb rast sa komik, tragjik, por edhe dometh\u00ebn\u00ebs.\nKur n\u00eb nj\u00eb nga motet e pun\u00ebs ILKPD, p\u00ebrfshiu n\u00eb shortin e filtrimit t\u00eb pasuris\u00eb Edi Ram\u00ebn, kryetar partie dhe Bashkie, ende i pab\u00ebr\u00eb kryeminist\u00ebr, ish- Ambasadori Amerikan John Withers ka ul\u00ebritur ndaj ekspert\u00ebve e drejtuesve t\u00eb ILKPD, p\u00ebrse e p\u00ebrfshin\u00eb Ram\u00ebn n\u00eb list\u00ebn e hetimit. Nuk duhet t\u00eb jet\u00eb, at\u00eb e di un\u00eb se un\u00eb jam numri nj\u00eb ktu\u2026Ka befasuar kedo ndodhej aty. Nd\u00ebrkoh\u00eb p\u00ebrzgjedhjen e b\u00ebnt\u00eb programi, q\u00eb ishte i gjithi investim i USAID, t\u00ebr\u00ebsisht kontroll amerikan. Drejtues t\u00eb USAID aso kohe u p\u00ebrfshin\u00eb n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb incident serioz duke u th\u00ebn\u00eb ILKPD se ambasadori nuk ka t\u00eb drejt\u00eb dhe ne jemi me ju, sepse keni respektuar procedur\u00ebn. Madje k\u00ebt\u00eb ngjarje dhe shqet\u00ebsim do ta p\u00ebrcjellim n\u00eb DASH.\nHistori t\u00eb tilla q\u00eb un\u00eb mund t\u00eb di, ka mjaft dhe plot\u2026\nNdaj kjo struktur\u00eb n\u00eb nj\u00eb far\u00eb m\u00ebnyre m\u00eb fort ngjan si nj\u00eb instrument p\u00ebr projekte rajonale dhe globale, ku guximtar\u00ebt duhet t\u00eb heshtin se SPAKU t\u00eb th\u00ebrret.\nVijm\u00eb te Pyetja 1 milion\u00eb dollar\u00ebshe ?\nCili prej t\u00eb 15 spakist\u00ebve ka kurajon profesionale pa asnj\u00eb paragjykim, frik\u00eb apo borxh, t\u00eb firmos\u00eb urdh\u00ebr-arreste p\u00ebr Edi Ram\u00ebn, Ilir Met\u00ebn, Sali Berish\u00ebn, Monika Kryemadhin, Lulzim Bash\u00ebn, Fatos Nanon,Guvernator\u00eb t\u00eb Bank\u00ebs s\u00eb Shqip\u00ebris\u00eb, Prokuror\u00ebt e P\u00ebrgjithsh\u00ebm, krer\u00ebt e gjykatave Kushtetuese dhe asaj t\u00eb Lart\u00eb, kupol\u00ebn drejtuese t\u00eb sistemit t\u00eb drejt\u00ebsis\u00eb dhe nj\u00eb turr\u00eb ministrash e deputetesh t\u00eb t\u00eb gjitha qeverive. Sepse k\u00ebta jan\u00eb p\u00ebrgjegj\u00ebsit p\u00ebr at\u00eb \u00e7ka \u00ebsht\u00eb b\u00ebr\u00eb dhe nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb b\u00ebr\u00eb, \u00e7ka \u00ebsht\u00eb vjedhur, grabitur, apo mbetur ende pa pla\u00e7kitur.??!\nMadje t\u00eb shohim dhe ndonj\u00eb nd\u00ebrkomb\u00ebtar s\u00eb paku \u201cnon grata\u201d se arrestimet jan\u00eb telash diplomatik, sepse kan\u00eb p\u00ebrlar\u00eb e p\u00ebrfituar t\u00eb paimagjinueshmen. Asnj\u00ebri prej tyre se ka b\u00ebr\u00eb p\u00ebr shpirt t\u00eb gjyshit apo t\u00eb ngat\u00ebrroj\u00eb hall\u00ebn me xhaj\u00ebn dhe daj\u00ebn.\nNj\u00ebher\u00ebh t\u00eb firmosin sekuestro pasurish, ngrirje llogarish, brenda dhe jasht\u00eb vendit. Kthim t\u00eb k\u00ebtyre pasurive e llogarive n\u00eb buxhetin e shtetit, rikthim sh\u00ebrbimesh e investimesh me k\u00ebto pasuri marramend\u00ebse.\nE b\u00ebjn\u00eb dot?\nAta e din\u00eb!\nN\u00ebse po, shqiptar\u00ebt do ju jen\u00eb mir\u00ebnjoh\u00ebs sepse kan\u00eb b\u00ebr\u00eb dicka p\u00ebr vendin. N\u00ebse jo. N\u00ebse filllojn\u00eb e p\u00ebrp\u00ebliten, kemi familje, kemi f\u00ebmij\u00eb, p\u00ebrse ne do \u00e7lirojm\u00eb Shqip\u00ebrin\u00eb, at\u00ebher\u00eb n\u00eb t\u00eb s\u00ebm\u00ebs.\nThjesht kemi ca rrogtar\u00eb m\u00eb tep\u00ebr, ca kurban\u00eb t\u00eb dor\u00ebs s\u00eb dyt\u00eb e t\u00eb tret\u00eb t\u00eb p\u00ebrkohsh\u00ebm.\nDosjet nuk mungojn\u00eb.\nBurrat dhe grat\u00eb q\u00eb kan\u00eb marr\u00eb p\u00ebrsip\u00ebr ta b\u00ebjn\u00eb duhet t\u00eb japin mesazhet se e b\u00ebjn\u00eb.\nSPAKU nis k\u00ebtu!\nT\u00eb tjerat jan\u00eb thjesht pordh\u00eb me rigon\u2026",
        "Kreu i opozit\u00ebs Lulzim Basha, n\u00eb takimin me strukturat e Partis\u00eb Demokratike n\u00eb Prrenjas deklaroi se n\u00eb fund t\u00eb k\u00ebsaj beteje, nuk do t\u00eb ket\u00eb vet\u00ebm rotacion politik, por fundi i tranzicionit.\nDuke drejtuar gishtin tek Edi Rama si fajtori kryesor p\u00ebr kriz\u00ebn ekonomike e sociale t\u00eb vendit, Basha tha se PD ka gati planin dhe programin p\u00ebr t\u00eb kthyer besimin e shqiptar\u00ebve tek qeverisja.\n\u201cBab\u00ebzia me t\u00eb cil\u00ebn Rama grabit buxhetin e shtetit, pasurin\u00eb e vendit, mineralet, naft\u00ebn, bregdetin, pyjet, uj\u00ebrat, guroret, gjith\u00e7ka \u00ebsht\u00eb arsyeja pse shqiptar\u00ebt jan\u00eb t\u00eb papun\u00eb, pse varf\u00ebria thellohet, nd\u00ebrsa Rama, Dako, Gjiknuri dhe Balla kridhen n\u00eb lluks dhe p\u00ebrvet\u00ebsojn\u00eb miliona euro\u201d \u2013 theksoi Basha.\n\u201cAsnj\u00eb plan tjet\u00ebr nuk ka Edi Rama dhe banda e tij p\u00ebrve\u00e7 grabitjes s\u00eb pasurive publike si te Teatri Komb\u00ebtar ku do t\u00eb p\u00ebrfitoj\u00eb 200 milion\u00eb euro me 6 kullat e drog\u00ebs. Asnj\u00eb ofert\u00eb zhvillimi p\u00ebrve\u00e7 grabitjes s\u00eb bregdetit nga Saranda dhe Himara n\u00eb Sh\u00ebngjin e Velipoj\u00eb. Milot-Balldreni, Unaza e Re jan\u00eb po ashtu grabitje me ligj e dhjet\u00ebra miliona eurove nga Edi Rama-\u201d tha Basha.\n\u201cBashk\u00eb me 85% t\u00eb shqiptar\u00ebve q\u00eb duan ndryshim, do ta largojm\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb band\u00eb. Vendi i tyre \u00ebsht\u00eb para drejt\u00ebsis\u00eb me pranga n\u00eb duar, nga i pari tek i fundit. Fundi i pand\u00ebshkueshm\u00ebris\u00eb s\u00eb pushtetar\u00ebve t\u00eb korruptuar e t\u00eb lidhur me krimin \u00ebsht\u00eb fillimi i Shqip\u00ebris\u00eb si gjith\u00eb Europa.\nNe e dim\u00eb q\u00eb n\u00eb fund t\u00eb k\u00ebsaj rruge nuk do t\u00eb kemi vet\u00ebm rrotacion politik por do t\u00eb kemi fundin e tranzicionit dhe Partin\u00eb Demokratike n\u00eb krye t\u00eb aleanc\u00ebs son\u00eb qeveris\u00ebse p\u00ebr t\u00eb hapur rrug\u00ebn e standardit t\u00eb v\u00ebrtet\u00eb europian, p\u00ebr t\u00eb b\u00ebr\u00eb realitet Shqip\u00ebrin\u00eb e standardit europian n\u00eb \u00e7do fush\u00eb.\nLargimi i Edi Ram\u00ebs \u00ebsht\u00eb kusht i par\u00eb dhe i panegociuesh\u00ebm. Vet\u00ebm nj\u00eb qeveri tranzitore pa Edi Ram\u00ebn kryeminist\u00ebr mund t\u00eb garantoj\u00eb vot\u00ebn e qytetar\u00ebt. Ne e dim\u00eb se me vot\u00eb t\u00eb lir\u00eb dhe t\u00eb ndershme, Rama \u00ebsht\u00eb larguar, PD \u00ebsht\u00eb n\u00eb krye t\u00eb qeverisjes s\u00eb ardhshme t\u00eb vendit,\u201d\u2013 u shpreh Basha.\nShefi i opozit\u00ebs n\u00ebnvizoi se farsa e 30 qershorit \u00ebsht\u00eb nul dhe deklaroi se PD dhe opozita do jen\u00eb n\u00eb krah t\u00eb qytetar\u00ebve p\u00ebr t\u00eb mbrojtur pushtetin lokal nga uzurpimi antikushtetues i tij.\n\u201cNe do t\u00eb q\u00ebndrojm\u00eb s\u00eb bashku, me t\u00eb gjitha format dhe m\u00ebnyrat, n\u00eb krah t\u00eb qytetar\u00ebve, p\u00ebr t\u00eb kund\u00ebrshtuar me t\u00eb gjitha format dhe m\u00ebnyrat uzurpimin e dhunsh\u00ebm t\u00eb pushtetit vendor.\nNe nuk pranojm\u00eb kurr\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb uzurpim antikushtetues dhe antiligjor.\nAty ku pushteti i paligjsh\u00ebm, i lindur nga vota e bler\u00eb me parat\u00eb e drog\u00ebs dhe t\u00eb krimit, p\u00ebrpiqet t\u00eb uzurpoj\u00eb pushtetin e ligjsh\u00ebm, pushtetin legjitim t\u00eb qytetar\u00ebve, aty, \u00e7do lloj forme rezistence \u00ebsht\u00eb legjitime, \u00ebsht\u00eb e p\u00ebrligjur, dhe ne jo vet\u00ebm nuk do ta frenojm\u00eb, por do ta inkurajojm\u00eb\u201d, \u2013 deklaroi kreu i opozit\u00ebs.\nKryetari i PD rikonfirmoi objektivin e opozit\u00ebs s\u00eb bashkuar q\u00eb zgjedhjet parlamentare t\u00eb parakohshme t\u00eb zhvillohen n\u00eb nj\u00eb dit\u00eb me zgjedhjet kushtetuese p\u00ebr pushtetin vendor.\nMe zgjedhje t\u00eb lira, theksoi Basha, shumica \u201cRama ik\u201d do ti jap\u00eb jet\u00eb nj\u00eb programi ekonomik p\u00ebr t\u00eb rim\u00ebk\u00ebmbur ekonomin\u00eb e Shqip\u00ebris\u00eb dhe p\u00ebr t\u00eb mbajtur p\u00ebrmes pun\u00ebsimit n\u00eb vendin e tyre t\u00eb rinjt\u00eb q\u00eb braktisin vendin nga keqqeverisja e band\u00ebs s\u00eb Rilindjes.\n\u201cJemi t\u00eb vendosur q\u00eb shumic\u00ebn \u201cRama ik\u201d t\u00eb 30 qershorit ta kthejm\u00eb n\u00eb forc\u00ebn e ndryshimit q\u00eb k\u00ebrkon \u00e7do shqiptar, q\u00eb do t\u2019i jap\u00eb fund braktisjes s\u00eb vendit p\u00ebr t\u2019u larguar n\u00eb emigracion, politikave t\u00eb shpun\u00ebsimit, shkat\u00ebrrimit t\u00eb ekonomis\u00eb.\nNe do t\u00eb mund\u00ebsojm\u00eb hapjen e mij\u00ebra vende pune n\u00eb sektor\u00eb t\u00eb pashfryt\u00ebzuar deri m\u00eb sot, me paga dinjitoze p\u00ebr rinin\u00eb shqiptare dhe zhvillimin ekonomik.\u201d \u2013 vuri theksin n\u00eb fjal\u00ebn e tij Basha.",
        "Botapress 21 Janar \u2013 Njoh\u00ebsit e \u00e7\u00ebshtjeve politike i kujtojn\u00eb Vet\u00ebvendosjes se askush nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb mbi Ligjin. Vendimi i Gjykat\u00ebs Kushtetuese e cila nuk lejon kandidimin e personave t\u00eb d\u00ebnuar gjat\u00eb tri viteve t\u00eb fundit ka v\u00ebn\u00eb n\u00eb pik\u00ebpyetje kandidimin e Albin Kurtit n\u00eb zgjedhjet e 14 shkurtit.\nAnalisti Fisnik Halimi thot\u00eb se L\u00ebvizja Vet\u00ebvendosje nuk do ta p\u00ebrfill vendimin e KQZ-s\u00eb p\u00ebr mos certifikimin eventual t\u00eb Kurtin n\u00eb zgjedhje. Megjithat\u00eb Halimi mendon se gara do t\u00eb d\u00ebmtohet n\u00ebse Kurti nuk garon n\u00eb zgjedhje.\n\u201cLejimi apo jo i Albin Kurtit dhe t\u00eb tjer\u00ebve nuk duhet t\u00eb b\u00ebhet tem\u00eb e k\u00ebsaj fushate zgjedhore. N\u00eb t\u00eb nj\u00ebjt\u00ebn koh\u00eb gara do t\u00eb d\u00ebmtohet shum\u00eb n\u00ebse Kurti nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb pjes\u00eb e gar\u00ebs. Mendoj se Vet\u00ebvendosje nuk do ta p\u00ebrfill k\u00ebt\u00eb vendim deri n\u00eb momentin e fundit dhe pastaj kur t\u00eb sosen t\u00eb gjitha afatet ligjore do ta p\u00ebrzgjedh nj\u00eb person t\u00eb dyt\u00eb nga lista e saj\u201d, deklaroi Fisnik Halimi, p\u00ebr RTV Dukagjinin.\nPublicisti Shkelzen Maliqi thot\u00eb se askush nuk duhet t\u00eb jet\u00eb mbi ligjin, dhe se Kurti nuk dallon nga 46 kandidat\u00ebt tjer\u00eb q\u00eb mund t\u00eb mos lejohen t\u00eb garojn\u00eb n\u00eb zgjedhje, p\u00ebrcjell Telegrafi.\n\u201cMendoj se askush nuk duhet t\u00eb jet\u00eb mbi ligjin. Kur \u00ebsht\u00eb d\u00ebnuar Kurti p\u00ebr hedhjen e gazit lotsjell\u00ebs, gjykat\u00ebsit kan\u00eb pasur konsiderat\u00eb p\u00ebr shkak se ishte shef i opozit\u00ebs dhe ia kan\u00eb dh\u00ebn\u00eb d\u00ebnimin me kusht\u201d.\nEdhe Zyra e BE-s\u00eb n\u00eb Kosov\u00eb ka reaguar p\u00ebr k\u00ebt\u00eb \u00e7\u00ebshtje duke th\u00ebn\u00eb se nuk duhet t\u00eb ket\u00eb nd\u00ebrhyrje n\u00eb pun\u00ebn e KQZ-s\u00eb.",
        "Dhimbje f\u00ebmij\u00ebn vjeti gjunj\u00eb\nGjunj\u00eb spraine kolateral ligament\n\u00c7far\u00eb \u00ebsht\u00eb t\u00ebrheqja p\u00ebrbashk\u00ebt\nOsteochondrosis qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs / / ' ) ; / / ] ] > Kjo s\u00ebmundje \u00ebsht\u00eb e lidhur me ndryshimet n\u00eb struktur\u00ebn e disqe intervertebral, i shoq\u00ebruar nga dhimbje t\u00eb vazhdueshme n\u00eb qaf\u00eb, tempuj dhe qaf\u00ebn. P\u00ebr asnj\u00eb arsye n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb organ muskulor disi t\u00eb prirur p\u00ebr mpirje. Le t\u00eb shikojm\u00eb n\u00eb shkaqet e mundshme t\u00eb dhimbjes n\u00ebn teh shpatull\u00ebn e majt\u00eb. Kjo dukuri \u00ebsht\u00eb tipike p\u00ebr shofer\u00ebt dhe pun\u00ebtor\u00ebt e zyr\u00ebs. Osteochondrosis Po, osteochondrosis e shpin\u00eb dhimbje t\u00eb qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs t\u00eb mundsh\u00ebm n\u00eb teh shpatull\u00ebn. Para s\u00eb gjithash \u00ebsht\u00eb e nevojshme p\u00ebr t\u00eb kuptuar se \u00e7far\u00eb ndikon n\u00eb shfaqjen e dhimbjes. Nj\u00eb tjet\u00ebr gj\u00eb, n\u00eb qoft\u00eb se ai \u00ebsht\u00eb shum\u00eb \" interesante\" apo t\u00eb tjera ( jo aq t\u00eb frikshme) Arsyet e detyroi at\u00eb t\u00eb jet\u00eb pa fjal\u00eb. Ajo \u00ebsht\u00eb shkaktuar nga nj\u00eb ulje kompensuese n\u00eb muskuj kurrizor. L\u00ebvizja e kok\u00ebs dhe qaf\u00ebs. Simptomat dhe shkalla e spondylolisthesis e shpin\u00eb qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs Pasojat e zhvendosjes. Formacioni i mundsh\u00ebm i nj\u00eb bllok funksional segment vertebral- motorike. Q\u00eb shtrihet n\u00eb vesh\u00ebt, qaf\u00ebn, nganj\u00ebher\u00eb n\u00eb nofull\u00ebn e poshtme dhe prapa.\nN\u00eb rastin e dhimbje koke t\u00eb qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs osteochondrosis lind nga fakti se arteria vertebral \u00ebsht\u00eb shtrydhur spikes plot hala. M\u00eb shum\u00eb deg\u00eb nervore q\u00eb t\u00eb b\u00ebhet i p\u00ebrflakur dhe i fryr\u00eb, rezultati \u00ebsht\u00eb dhimbje koke. Zhvendosja e rruaza t\u00eb nj\u00eb foshnj\u00ebrin\u00eb e f\u00ebmij\u00ebve lidhur me nj\u00eb l\u00ebvizje t\u00eb mpreht\u00eb t\u00eb kok\u00ebs prapa;. Kur osteochondrosis e shpin\u00eb qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs \u00ebsht\u00eb shpesh n\u00eb ana e kok\u00ebs, osteochondrosis mesit - gjat\u00eb bust. N\u00eb qoft\u00eb se u shkall\u00ebzua osteokondroza qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs, dhimbje q\u00eb dalin n\u00eb qaf\u00eb, mu n\u00eb krah, e cila \u00ebsht\u00eb e v\u00ebshtir\u00eb dhe e dhimbshme p\u00ebr t\u00eb l\u00ebvizur; Rrall\u00eb. Stresi intelektuale ose fizike, e cila shpesh shfaqet pas nj\u00eb pune t\u00eb gjat\u00eb n\u00eb pozit\u00eb t\u00eb pak\u00ebndshme.\nOsteokondroza Ndonj\u00ebher\u00eb i qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs \u00ebsht\u00eb quajtur vertebrobazylyarn\u044by sindromi. N\u00eb shumic\u00ebn e rasteve operacioni \u00ebsht\u00eb shum\u00eb efektiv, por penges\u00eb e saj \u00ebsht\u00eb se provokuar zhvillimin e komplikimeve dhe. Simptomet e migren\u00eb t\u00eb qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs P\u00ebr t\u00eb filluar, ne v\u00ebrejm\u00eb se migren\u00eb i qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs ndodh periodikisht, k\u00ebshtu q\u00eb simptomat zhduken pas nj\u00eb koh\u00eb. Por n\u00eb qoft\u00eb se faza e s\u00ebmundjes \u00ebsht\u00eb tashm\u00eb running, ajo tregon se pacienti do t\u00eb shikojn\u00eb shum\u00eb shpesh.\nN\u00eb raste t\u00eb tilla ka shpesh dhimbje kur l\u00ebviz kok\u00ebn. Shum\u00eb s\u00ebmundje t\u00eb qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs shpin\u00eb shkaktojn\u00eb dhimbje qafe dhe prapa. N\u00eb var\u00ebsi t\u00eb zon\u00ebs dhe shkall\u00ebs s\u00eb simptomave compression mund t\u00eb ndryshojn\u00eb shum\u00eb, k\u00ebshtu q\u00eb \u00ebsht\u00eb e r\u00ebnd\u00ebsishme n\u00eb dyshimin e par\u00eb t\u00eb pajisjeve osteochondrosis b\u00ebr\u00eb k\u00ebrkime dhe v\u00ebn\u00eb diagnoz\u00eb t\u00eb. Por, para se k\u00ebto dhimbje zakonisht t\u00eb par\u00eb duket e zymt\u00eb, dhimbje shurdh\u00ebr n\u00eb zon\u00ebn e kok\u00ebs, qaf\u00ebs. Video: osteochondrosis qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs si personi mpirje shkaktoj\u00eb \" Impatient\" Gjuha. Dhimbje n\u00eb qaf\u00eb dhe rajonin e sip\u00ebrme t\u00eb qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs \u00ebsht\u00eb shum\u00eb e dhimbshme, n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb rast \u00ebsht\u00eb e v\u00ebshtir\u00eb t\u00eb thuhet me sakt\u00ebsi se \u00ebsht\u00eb me t\u00eb v\u00ebrtet\u00eb qaf\u00ebn l\u00ebnduar apo kok\u00eb.\nOsteochondrosis qaf\u00ebs s\u00eb mitr\u00ebs \u00ebsht\u00eb shum\u00eb e l\u00ebnduar prapa kok\u00ebs. Simptomat e saj jan\u00eb manifestime vestibular ( tring\u00ebllim\u00eb n\u00eb vesh\u00ebt, marramendje, duken mbuluar, \u00e7rregullime t\u00eb tjera t\u00eb vizionit dhe t\u00eb d\u00ebgjimit), mbrapa l\u00ebnduar e kok\u00ebs.",
        "Xhamiat\nXhamia e par\u00eb n\u00eb Kraj\u00eb konsiderohet se \u00ebsht\u00eb Xhamia e Qyrjanit e nd\u00ebrtuar m\u00eb 1602. Sipas teologut Agoviq, xhamia e par\u00eb n\u00eb Kraj\u00eb \u00ebsht\u00eb nd\u00ebrtuar n\u00eb Muriq Nalt\u00eb. Mir\u00ebpo duke u bazaur n\u00eb faktet historike se Islamizmi n\u00eb Kraj\u00eb s\u00eb pari depertoi nga Shkodra, si rrjedhim logjik del se Xhamia e Qyrjanit duhet t\u00eb jet\u00eb ndonj\u00eb vit m\u00eb e vjet\u00ebr se e Muriqit Nalt\u00eb.\nXhami n\u00eb Kraj\u00eb ka n\u00eb: Skje, Arbnesh, Ostross t\u00eb Madh, Ostros t\u00eb Vog\u00ebl (Xhamia e re), Qyrjan, Runj, Bobosht, K\u00ebshtenj\u00eb, Ftjan , Muriq Nalt, Muriq Posht\u00eb dhe n\u00eb Bes.\nXhamia e Qyrjanit s\u00eb bashku me t\u00eb gjitha xhamiat e tjera t\u00eb Kraj\u00ebs p\u00ebrve\u00e7 q\u00eb sh\u00ebrbejn\u00eb si objekte kulti, ato leht\u00ebsisht mund t\u00eb konsiderohen monumente historike t\u00eb cilat bartin me vet\u00eb historin\u00eb e pushtimit osman n\u00eb k\u00ebto an\u00eb.",
        "Sht\u00ebpi pushimesh me qira n\u00eb Bettwil\nGjej dhe prenoto akomodime unike n\u00eb Airbnb\nSht\u00ebpi pushimesh me qira me vler\u00ebsime m\u00eb t\u00eb mira n\u00eb Bettwil\nVizitor\u00ebt e pranojn\u00eb: k\u00ebto q\u00ebndrime kan\u00eb vler\u00ebsime t\u00eb larta p\u00ebr vendndodhjen, past\u00ebrtin\u00eb e m\u00eb shum\u00eb.\nSuperprit\u00ebs\nApartament n\u00eb Gelfingen\nMidis liqenit dhe k\u00ebshtjell\u00ebs n\u00eb zem\u00ebr t\u00eb Zvicr\u00ebs\nMidis liqenit dhe k\u00ebshtjell\u00ebs, Lucernit dhe Zyrihut. N\u00eb zem\u00ebr t\u00eb Zvicr\u00ebs. Apartament komod, 2 ,5 dhoma (65m2). Me kopsht privat p\u00ebr barbekju, ngr\u00ebnie dhe relaksim n\u00eb sallon. I p\u00ebrshtatsh\u00ebm p\u00ebr 4 miq ose nj\u00eb familje t\u00eb re. N\u00eb Gelfingen idilike, ajo ka gjith\u00e7ka q\u00eb d\u00ebshiron zemra jote - duke notuar n\u00eb liqen, ecje n\u00eb pyll, skijim n\u00eb Alpe, eksplorim t\u00eb qyteteve t\u00eb famshme zvicerane (Basel, Bern, Zyrih. Familje miq\u00ebsore dhe shum\u00ebgjuh\u00ebshe prit\u00ebse. Super e pajisur - Super e pajisur - wifi, lavatri\u00e7e, edhe krevat f\u00ebmij\u00ebsh).\n$103 p\u00ebr nat\u00eb\nSuperprit\u00ebs\nApartament n\u00eb Z\u00fcrich\nQyteti i vjet\u00ebr i Zyrihut\nN\u00eb zem\u00ebr t\u00eb qytetit t\u00eb vjet\u00ebr t\u00eb Zyrihut. E p\u00ebrkryer p\u00ebr udh\u00ebtar\u00ebt beqar\u00eb, nj\u00eb \u00e7ift ose biznes. Nuk ka vendndodhje m\u00eb t\u00eb mir\u00eb n\u00eb Zyrih. Nga stacioni kryesor i Zyrihut p\u00ebr 5 minuta n\u00eb k\u00ebmb\u00eb. Nga aeroporti i Zyrihut me tren p\u00ebr 15 minuta. Pran\u00eb lumit, liqenit, restoranteve, kinemave dhe rrug\u00ebve tregtare. Apartamenti i vog\u00ebl i bukur ndodhet n\u00eb katin e dyt\u00eb, me krevat, dush, tualet, televizor, wifi, kuzhin\u00eb. Prit\u00ebsi \u00ebsht\u00eb i k\u00ebnaqur t\u00eb k\u00ebshilloj\u00eb p\u00ebr restorante, arg\u00ebtim dhe vizita turistike gjat\u00eb gjith\u00eb koh\u00ebs.\n$130 p\u00ebr nat\u00eb\nSuperprit\u00ebs\nSuita e vizitor\u00ebve n\u00eb Muri\nGrosses, helles Studio n\u00eb Muri, Kanton Aargau\nMir\u00eb se vjen! Studioja e ndritshme (rreth 37 metra katror\u00eb) ndodhet n\u00eb nj\u00eb sht\u00ebpi t\u00eb qet\u00eb e t\u00eb shk\u00ebputur n\u00eb Muri, Canton Aargau. Studio \u00ebsht\u00eb e pajisur me nj\u00eb krevat dopio, nj\u00eb tavolin\u00eb me 2 karrige, nj\u00eb gard\u00ebrob\u00eb t\u00eb madhe, nj\u00eb divan, nj\u00eb kolltuk, nj\u00eb raft, nj\u00eb kuzhin\u00eb t\u00eb vog\u00ebl (pa furr\u00eb), frigorifer dhe Wi-Fi. Banj\u00eb me dush/tualet. Hap\u00ebsira e parkimit q\u00eb i p\u00ebrket studios ndodhet drejtp\u00ebrdrejt para hyrjes s\u00eb ve\u00e7ant\u00eb. Zon\u00eb e vog\u00ebl m\u00eb vete p\u00ebr t 'u ulur n\u00eb kopsht.\n$80 p\u00ebr nat\u00eb\nSht\u00ebpi pushimesh me qira p\u00ebr \u00e7do stil\nMerr aq hap\u00ebsir\u00eb sa t\u00eb jet\u00eb e p\u00ebrshtatshme p\u00ebr ty.\nSht\u00ebpi t\u00eb tjera pushimesh me qira n\u00eb Bettwil\nPo shfaqim 0 nga 0 artikuj\n1 nga 3 faqe\n1 nga 3 faqe",
        "Tirana festoi Halloween n\u00eb dekorin e Iceberg\nHallouin u festua kudo n\u00eb baret dhe lokalet e kryeqytetit. T\u00eb rinjt\u00eb u shfaq\u00ebn me maska nga m\u00eb t\u00eb thjeshtat deri n\u00eb ato m\u00eb t\u00eb \u00e7uditshmet. Ndodh shpesh q\u00eb na duhet t\u00eb vem\u00eb nj\u00eb mask\u00eb t\u00eb padukshme. Por ka nj\u00eb dit\u00eb kur mund t\u00eb mbajm\u00eb nj\u00eb t\u00eb v\u00ebrtet\u00eb. N\u00eb dit\u00ebn e Halloween-it Tirana mbushet me plot syresh. \u00cbsht\u00eb nj\u00eb gar\u00eb p\u00ebr mask\u00ebn apo veshjen m\u00eb t\u00eb frikshme. Halloween besohet t\u00eb jet\u00eb dita kur shpirtrat e atyre q\u00eb kan\u00eb vdekur vitin e m\u00ebparsh\u00ebm do t\u00eb kthehen p\u00ebr t\u00eb z\u00ebn\u00eb vend n\u00eb trupin e nj\u00eb t\u00eb gjalli. Festimet nisin q\u00eb n\u00eb dat\u00ebn 29 tetor, me simbolin kryesor t\u00eb fest\u00ebs s\u00eb vjesht\u00ebs q\u00eb jan\u00eb kungujt e ndri\u00e7uar. Ashtu si vitet e kaluara dekoret origjinale t\u00eb Iceberg Dekor ishin ato qe ran\u00eb n\u00eb sy dhe krijuan atmosfer\u00ebn e vecant\u00eb n\u00eb baret dhe lokalet e Tiran\u00ebs.\nBurrimi: abcnews.al",
        "Pavar\u00ebsisht asaj s\u00eb HTC One Max ende nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb prezantuar zyrtarisht, kompania nuk ka mundur ta ndal kryeshefin e saj nga publikimi i disa imazheve t\u00eb k\u00ebtij modeli.\nPeter Chou \u00ebsht\u00eb i njohur edhe me her\u00ebt p\u00ebr at\u00eb se nuk ka mundur t\u00eb pres deri t\u00eb paraqitja zyrtare e modeleve t\u00eb reja t\u00eb smartphone-ve, dukur i shfaqur imazhet e pajisjeve t\u00eb reja t\u00eb tyre, ngjash\u00ebm edhe k\u00ebsaj radhe e ka b\u00ebr\u00eb me modelin HTC One Max. N\u00eb nj\u00eb postim n\u00eb nj\u00eb uebfaqe kineze t\u00eb internetit Xuite, Chou ka shfaqur disa imazhe t\u00eb detajuara t\u00eb HTC One Max. K\u00ebto foto tregojn\u00eb skanerin p\u00ebr gjurm\u00eb gishtash, si dhe disa pamje t\u00eb dizajnit p\u00ebrreth.\nEnde nuk dihet se kur do t\u00eb lansohet ky model, mir\u00ebpo p\u00ebrderisa Chou ka publikuar k\u00ebto imazhe at\u00ebher\u00eb sigurisht se nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb larg. |ameble|",
        "Misioni i Urdhrit t\u00eb Stomatologeve \u00ebsht\u00eb ruajtja e standardeve t\u00eb larta n\u00eb formimin dhe ushtrimin e profesionit te stomatologut dhe mbrojtja e pacient\u00ebve dhe publikut nga kequshtrimi i ketij profesioni.\nT\u00eb nderuar koleg\u00eb Ju njoftojm\u00eb se Urdhri i Stomatologut t\u00eb Shqip\u00ebris\u00eb organizon trajnimin e pare on-line me leksione, t\u00eb titulluar \u201cNjohuri Etiko-Legjislative p\u00ebr Mjek\u00ebt Stomatolog\u00eb\u201d. Ky aktivitet \u00ebsht\u00eb i njohur nga Q.K.E.V. dhe \u00ebsht\u00eb vler\u00ebsuar paraprakisht me 9 kredite. Si\u00e7 vet\u00ebkuptohet nga titulli, ky trajnim do t\u00eb ofroj\u00eb nj\u00eb azhornim njohurish juridike dhe proceduriale p\u00ebr\nTarifat e an\u00ebtar\u00ebsis\u00eb p\u00ebr an\u00ebtar\u00ebt e Urdhrit t\u00eb Stomatologut do t\u00eb jen\u00eb si vijon: Deri n\u00eb muajin Maj 2015 me tarif\u00ebn 200 lek\u00eb t\u00eb reja n\u00eb muaj dhe m\u00eb pas jan\u00eb 1000 lek\u00eb t\u00eb reja n\u00eb muaj. Nga muaji Maj 2015 dhe ne vazhdim,kuota e anetaresise eshte 1000 leke te reja ne muaj mbeshtetur mbi",
        "Cilado qoft\u00eb metoda e depilimit q\u00eb p\u00ebrdorni, asnj\u00ebher\u00eb qimet nuk do t\u00eb zhduken p\u00ebrjet\u00ebsisht nga trupi juaj ! T\u00eb jet\u00eb vall\u00eb kjo arsyeja p\u00ebrse femrat rrin\u00eb gjith\u00eb dit\u00ebn me piskatore n\u00eb dor\u00eb? Tek tuk t\u00eb gjith\u00eb e kan\u00eb nga njq qime n\u00eb mjek\u00ebr, n\u00eb fytyr\u00eb apo n\u00eb kraharor, por p\u00ebrpara se t\u00eb p\u00ebrdorni piskatoren n\u00eb k\u00ebto pjes\u00eb t\u00eb trupit duhet t\u00eb mendoheni dy her\u00eb.\nJoshua Zeichner nj\u00eb dermatologe e certifikuar n\u00eb Ne\u00eb York n\u00eb nj\u00eb intervist\u00eb p\u00ebr \u00cbomen\u2019s Health shprehet se heqja e qimeve me piskatore mund t\u00eb shkaktoj\u00eb inflamim t\u00eb rr\u00ebnj\u00ebs n\u00ebse piskatorja nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb e sterilizuar.\nThithkat e gjoksit\nNuk \u00ebsht\u00eb \u00e7udi q\u00eb rreth thithkave t\u00eb gjoksit t\u00eb rriten qime t\u00eb holla. Kjo \u00ebsht\u00eb natyrale dhe pse shum\u00eb femra nuk do t\u00eb donin t\u2019i kishin. Piskatorja mund t\u00eb irritoj\u00eb l\u00ebkur\u00ebn n\u00ebse ju e ngacmoni k\u00ebt\u00eb t\u00eb fundit, ndaj m\u00ebnyra m\u00eb e mir\u00eb \u00ebsht\u00eb q\u00eb k\u00ebto qime t\u2019i prisni me g\u00ebrsh\u00ebr\u00eb.\nNishane\nN\u00ebse nuk d\u00ebshironi q\u00eb nishan\u00ebt e trupit t\u00eb mos ju infektohen, mbajeni larg pistaroen nga k\u00ebta t\u00eb fundit.\nPu\u00e7rrat apo aknet\n\u00cbsht\u00eb shum\u00eb e zakonshme q\u00eb qimet n\u00ebn l\u00ebkur\u00eb t\u00eb inflamohen. N\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb rast \u00ebsht\u00eb i nevojshm\u00eb pastrim i il\u00ebkur\u00ebs dhe heqja e qimes me rr\u00ebnj\u00eb, por n\u00ebse kjo pu\u00e7\u00ebrr \u00ebsht\u00eb nj\u00eb akne qimja nuk duhet hequr. N\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb m\u00ebnyr\u00eb ju do t\u00eb rrisni mund\u00ebsin\u00eb p\u00ebr zhvillimin e infeksionit duke mbledhur qelb dhe duke mbledhur bakteret. M\u00ebnyra m\u00eb e mir\u00eb \u00ebsht\u00eb t\u00eb prisni deri sa pu\u00e7rra t\u00eb thahet e t\u00eb eksfoljoi l\u00ebkur\u00ebn derisa qimja t\u00eb dal\u00eb vet\u00eb n\u00eb sip\u00ebrfaqe\nBurimi: Women's Health",
        "Ja kur publikohet projekti i ri i Nora Istrefit\nK\u00ebnga e re e Nora Istrefit \u2018Maj\u00ebm\u2019 q\u00eb po pritet me padurim nga fansat duket se tek e treta e v\u00ebrteta, do publikohet sot n\u00eb or\u00ebn 17:00.\nKy \u00ebsht\u00eb afati i ri t\u00eb cilin e ka m\u00ebsuar Prive, pas shtyerjes q\u00eb nga burime af\u00ebr k\u00ebng\u00ebtares u tha se ndodhi shkaku i disa problemeve t\u00eb paparashikueshme t\u00eb karakterit teknik.\nKujtojm\u00eb se \u2018Maj\u00ebm\u2019 p\u00ebrb\u00ebn nj\u00eb projekt gjigant tek i cili jan\u00eb p\u00ebrfshir\u00eb shum\u00eb emra n\u00eb tekst e refren, me Cricketin n\u00eb krye, si \u2018truri\u2019 pas shum\u00eb hiteve dy vitet e fundit n\u00eb diskografin\u00eb shqiptare.",
        "Nga Frrok \u00c7upi\nL\u00ebvozhga?\u2026 Vet\u00eb PD, n\u00eb nj\u00eb kuptim, \u00ebsht\u00eb simbol i arr\u00ebs. Kur shikoj si po \u2018q\u00ebrohet\u2019 e vjetra n\u00eb PD, m\u00eb vjen n\u00eb mendje nj\u00eb nga motot e qeverisjes Berisha. Ai pat th\u00ebn\u00eb pafund\u00ebsisht: \u2018Mbjellim arror\u00eb, arror\u00eb, t\u00eb mbjellim arror\u00eb!\u2019. Dhe ja tani po q\u00ebrohen frutat dhe po bien gjethet e vjetra politike.\nKryetari i PD e p\u00ebrdori pa vend fjal\u00ebn \u2018llum\u2019, nd\u00ebrsa deputeti i vet\u00eb- gjetur si \u2018llum\u2019 k\u00ebrc\u00ebnoi, jo pse u fye, por sepse nuk e shikonte veten si \u2018llum\u2019. N\u00eb fakt, procesi q\u00eb po ndodh tani n\u00eb PD nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb proces i \u2018llumit\u2019, por \u00ebsht\u00eb proces i \u2018r\u00ebnies s\u00eb l\u00ebvozhg\u00ebs\u2019. Kryetari i PD kur i sulmoi si \u2018llum\u2019 e b\u00ebri kot dhe trembi njer\u00ebzit. Masa e dherave n\u00eb rrug\u00eb p\u00ebr shembull, si masa q\u00eb ra sot n\u00eb rrug\u00ebn e re t\u00eb Lumit t\u00eb Vlor\u00ebs dhe ku denoncoi nj\u00eb demokrat, (kjo quhet llum) i frik\u00ebson njer\u00ebzit. PD tani nuk frik\u00ebson m\u00eb njeri, dhe prandaj nuk mund t\u00eb p\u00ebrdoret fjala q\u00eb n\u00ebnkupton rrezikun e dherave e t\u00eb balt\u00ebs. Q\u00eb n\u00eb momentin kur Shtetet e Bashkuara \u00e7montoi rrezikun \u2018Berisha\u2019, q\u00eb aty u pa se PD nuk ka m\u00eb dh\u00ebmb\u00eb; tani rrokulliset si arrat n\u00eb vjesht\u00eb. Tani Berisha as mund t\u00eb b\u00ebhet kryetar n\u00eb PD, as kryeminist\u00ebr e as brigadier pulash, as t\u00eb vras\u00eb e as t\u00eb djeg\u00eb vendin. Q\u00eb nga 19 maji, kur u godit nga Amerika, klika e tij po l\u00ebshon l\u00ebkur\u00ebn.\nL\u00ebvozhga po q\u00ebrohet pjes\u00eb- pjes\u00eb dhe me kujdes:\nHiqet fillimisht gjerdani i kapsollave.\nNj\u00ebsoj si n\u00eb sht\u00ebpit\u00eb e vjetra me hasm\u00ebri kur dikush vjen i armatosur dhe l\u00ebshon gjerdanin. Dje u shkarkua n\u00ebnkryetari i komisionit t\u00eb Siguris\u00eb, Noka. U shkarkua nga \u2018komisioni i siguris\u00eb\u2019, por jo nga detyrat e larta politike. Ai \u00ebsht\u00eb an\u00ebtar i Byros\u00eb Politike, an\u00ebtar i Komitetit Qendror\u2019 n\u00eb PD\u2026, etj; por nuk u hoq prej andej. U q\u00ebrua thjesht nga \u2018Siguria\u2019. E di pse ndodh k\u00ebshtu? Sepse k\u00ebta q\u00eb jan\u00eb mish e thua me Berish\u00ebn, nuk duhet t\u00eb ken\u00eb lidhje me Sigurin\u00eb; me sup\u00ebn e me t\u00eb tjera, it\u2019s ok. Vet\u00eb Berisha \u00ebsht\u00eb n\u00ebn v\u00ebzhgim nga Shtetet e Bashkuara si rrezik p\u00ebr \u2018Sigurin\u00eb\u2019. Q\u00eb prej vitit 2017, n\u00eb PD dhe LSI nisi p\u00ebrgatitja e molotov\u00ebve dhe atentateve, si n\u00eb koh\u00ebn e terrorizmit t\u00eb \u2018Berish\u00ebs s\u00eb par\u00eb\u2019. N\u00eb fillim t\u00eb vitit 2021 n\u00eb vendin ton\u00eb u zhvillua manovra m\u00eb e madhe e ushtris\u00eb amerikane dhe iu d\u00ebshmoi \u2018arror\u00ebve\u2019 t\u00eb k\u00ebtush\u00ebm: \u201cEeej, jemi k\u00ebtu!\u201d. Gjat\u00eb gjith\u00eb koh\u00ebs Aleati i Madh \u00ebsht\u00eb me syrin mbi faktor\u00ebt q\u00eb duan t\u00eb sjellin konflikt, terroriz\u00ebm dhe kaos\u2026 Ja, p\u00ebr k\u00ebt\u00eb arsye, ata q\u00eb kan\u00eb lidhje me t\u00eb kaluar\u00ebn n\u00eb PD, \u2018q\u00ebrohen\u2019 si l\u00ebvozhg\u00eb, nga Siguria fillimisht; me t\u00eb tjerat le t\u00eb vijn\u00eb v\u00ebrdall\u00eb sa t\u00eb duan, nga Kuk\u00ebsi n\u00eb Gjirokast\u00ebr.\nPo zhvishet klika q\u00eb u zhyt n\u00eb korrupsion:\nShikoni kush po turfullon pse u p\u00ebrjashtua Berisha nga Grupi Parlamentar\u2026, pastaj Noka, pas Nok\u00ebs nj\u00eb Nok\u00eb tjet\u00ebr\u2026 Jan\u00eb ministrat, z\u00ebvend\u00ebsit, drejtor\u00ebt ose edhe vet\u00eb kryetarja e Kuvendit dhe Presidenti. T\u00eb pakt\u00ebn tet\u00eb vjet\u00ebt e fundit k\u00ebta u zhyt\u00ebn n\u00eb grabitje e n\u00eb korrupsion t\u00eb papar\u00eb, derisa i q\u00ebruan me vot\u00eb. Tregojn\u00eb bojaxhinjt\u00eb se kur hyjn\u00eb n\u00eb sht\u00ebpit\u00eb e tyre qelbet er\u00eb \u2018dollar\u00eb i ndenjur\u2019 n\u00eb dyshek\u00eb. Vet\u00eb Muli q\u00eb u shkarkua nga \u2018Siguria\u2019 paska deklaruar se ka mbi 5 milion\u00eb euro. Gjat\u00eb tet\u00eb vjet\u00ebve n\u00eb qeverisje nuk mbeti asgj\u00eb p\u00ebr vendin, p\u00ebrve\u00e7 500 met\u00ebr katror tort\u00eb dhe nj\u00eb shqiponj\u00eb e rrafsh\u00ebt n\u00eb Laprak\u00eb. Edhe nga 20 milion\u00eb arrat q\u00eb mbolli Berisha n\u00eb vitin 2011, sot nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb asnj\u00eb p\u00ebr b\u00e8\u2026\nK\u00ebta po tremben t\u00eb gjith\u00eb bash prej k\u00ebsaj katastrofe. Strazimiri u tremb dje e tha \u2018ky \u00ebsht\u00eb alarm i kuq\u2019. Shehu i famsh\u00ebm i preshit n\u00eb Lushnj\u00eb tregoi \u2018nderin lakuriq\u2019 e tha se \u2018un\u00eb e Berisha kemi dh\u00ebn\u00eb dor\u00ebheqjen, q\u00ebrohuni edhe ju\u2019. Jozi \u00ebsht\u00eb trishtuar katolikisht me fatin e Mulit dhe ka th\u00ebn\u00eb se \u2018e mbyti Ram\u00ebn, prandaj\u2026\u2019. Spaho thot\u00eb se shikon nj\u00eb \u2018litar\u2019, por nuk thot\u00eb ku\u2026 T\u00eb gjitha perceptimet jan\u00eb me shk\u00ebrmoqjen, o si l\u00ebvozhg\u00eb, o si k\u00ebrp litari, o si presh, o si \u2018mbytje\u2019. N\u00eb fakt kjo q\u00eb po ndodh \u00ebsht\u00eb ndarja e Partis\u00eb Demokratike nga kasta e vjet\u00ebr dhe e degraduar.\nPo q\u00ebrohet Luli nga \u2018parazit\u00ebt\u2019.\nLulzim Basha ka hyr\u00eb n\u00eb rrug\u00ebn p\u00ebr t\u2019u b\u00ebr\u00eb kryetar i v\u00ebrtet\u00eb i PD. Dje, kur foli p\u00ebr \u2018llumin e qeverisjes s\u00eb PD\u2019 q\u00eb \u2018po lan parat\u00eb n\u00eb Tiran\u00eb\u2019, foli me Berish\u00ebn. Berisha \u00ebsht\u00eb i treguar me gishtin e Amerik\u00ebs si i korruptuar, si lar\u00ebse parash me t\u00eb bijt\u00eb dhe si min\u00eb p\u00ebr shtetin demokratik. Luli e di mir\u00eb \u00e7far\u00eb e pret Berish\u00ebn dhe po shk\u00ebputet prej tij, q\u00eb t\u00eb mos e marr\u00eb p\u00ebrroi. Nd\u00ebrkoh\u00eb po jep sinjale se do t\u00eb nd\u00ebrtoj\u00eb nj\u00eb PD pa berishiz\u00ebm, pa histori krimi, pa biografi terrori, pa lidhje me terrorizmin, pa urrejtje ndaj shqiptar\u00ebve, pa mashtrim e vulgaritet. Luli ka aleat Shtetet e Bashkuara edhe p\u00ebr formimin e v\u00ebrtet\u00eb t\u00eb PD.\nPasi frutit t\u2019i bjer\u00eb l\u00ebvozhga e vjet\u00ebr, at\u00ebher\u00eb do t\u00eb ndodh\u00eb kjo.\nDo t\u00eb ishte mundimi m\u00eb i madh, nj\u00ebsoj si mundimi i Sizifit, p\u00ebr t\u00eb mb\u00ebrritur n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb maj\u00eb, sigurisht. Por Basha me sa duket, ka shansin e \u2018sendeve t\u00eb vjetra\u2019. K\u00ebta po bien vet\u00eb, nj\u00eb nga nj\u00eb, po ziejn\u00eb, po sh\u00ebmtohen dhe po shkojn\u00eb n\u00ebp\u00ebr uj\u00ebra\u2026 Kjo \u00ebsht\u00eb vjeshta politike e k\u00ebtij viti. Askush nuk mund t\u00eb thot\u00eb se p\u00ebr sa koh\u00eb do t\u00eb pastrohet PD nga \u2018parazit\u00ebt\u2019 q\u00eb l\u00ebvrijn\u00eb n\u00ebn sqetulla. As vet\u00eb qeveria e PD nuk mund ta dinte at\u00ebher\u00eb, kur hodhi parull\u00ebn mashtruese p\u00ebr mbjelljen e arroreve, se nj\u00eb dit\u00eb do ta gjente veten thjesht nj\u00eb l\u00ebvozhg\u00eb.\nPor ja ku jemi, po ndodh dhe k\u00ebta po ul\u00ebrijn\u00eb nga shk\u00ebrmoqja.",
        "BIRN Kosova\nBIRN Kosova \u00ebsht\u00eb pjes\u00eb Rrjetit Rajonal p\u00ebr Gazetari Hulumtuese me prezenc\u00eb n\u00eb t\u00eb gjith\u00eb Ballkanin\nT\u00eb gjitha sallat e operacionit n\u00eb Qendr\u00ebn Klinike Universitare t\u00eb Kosov\u00ebs, p\u00ebrfshir\u00eb edhe Klinik\u00ebn e Urologjis\u00eb, kan\u00eb punuar dhe po punojn\u00eb me kapacitete t\u00eb plota, pas furnizimit me sasi t\u00eb bollshme t\u00eb anestetik\u00ebve nga ana e Ministris\u00eb s\u00eb Sh\u00ebndet\u00ebsis\u00eb, njofton Sh\u00ebrbimi Spitalor Klinik Universitar i Kosov\u00ebs. \u201cBazuar n\u00eb informatat nga drejtoria e Klinik\u00ebs s\u00eb Anestezionit dhe Mjekimit Intensiv, por edhe nga drejtoria e Klinik\u00ebs s\u00eb Urologjis\u00eb, t\u00eb gjitha sallat e operacionit kan\u00eb punuar me kapacitet t\u00eb plot\u00eb. Shkrimi i sot\u00ebm i gazet\u00ebs \u201cZ\u00ebri\u201d \u00ebsht\u00eb tendencioz dhe\u2026\nNj\u00eb grua \u00ebsht\u00eb sulmuar nga tre persona n\u00eb sht\u00ebpin\u00eb e saj. Policia e Kosov\u00ebs njoftoi se dje rreth or\u00ebs 17 n\u00eb fshatin Hajvali n\u00eb Prishtin\u00eb nj\u00eb grua \u00ebsht\u00eb sulmuar dhe ngacmuar n\u00eb sht\u00ebpin\u00eb e saj nga tre persona t\u00eb dyshuar, dy meshkuj dhe nj\u00eb fem\u00ebr. Pas intervistimit me urdh\u00ebr t\u00eb prokurorit , t\u00eb dyshuarit jan\u00eb liruar n\u00eb procedur\u00eb t\u00eb rregullt.\nNj\u00eb person ka raportuar n\u00eb polici se ka hasur n\u00eb mjete t\u00eb dyshimta t\u00eb pashp\u00ebrthyera. Rasti ka ndodhur dje rreth or\u00ebs 16 n\u00eb fshatin Prelluzh\u00eb t\u00eb Vushtrris\u00eb. N\u00eb vendin e ngjarjes kan\u00eb dalur nj\u00ebsia p\u00ebr deminim e FSK-s\u00eb dhe KFOR-i amerikan t\u00eb cil\u00ebt i kan\u00eb marr\u00eb me vete mjetet e dyshimta. Sipas tyre kan\u00eb qen\u00eb tri raketa hedh\u00ebse me predha t\u00eb prodhimit jugosllav.\nNj\u00eb aksident trafiku mes nj\u00eb traktori dhe nj\u00eb bi\u00e7iklete ka ndodhur n\u00eb fshatin Kabash t\u00eb Vitis\u00eb. Policia ka njoftuar se dje rreth or\u00ebs 16, nj\u00eb person duke drejtuar traktorin e tij nga pakujdesia ka goditur drejtuesin e bi\u00e7iklet\u00ebs , duke i shkaktuar l\u00ebndime trupore. Viktim\u00ebs i \u00ebsht\u00eb dh\u00ebn\u00eb ndihma mjek\u00ebsore n\u00eb spitalin rajonal n\u00eb Gjilan , pastaj \u00ebsht\u00eb transferuar n\u00eb QKUK n\u00eb Prishtin\u00eb. Pas intervistimit me urdh\u00ebr t\u00eb prokurorit i dyshuari \u00ebsht\u00eb d\u00ebrguar n\u00eb mbajtje.\nSend this to a friend",
        "Ky burr\u00eb kthehet n\u00eb sht\u00ebpi i DEHUR, ajo \u00e7far\u00eb i ndodh me gruan nuk e keni d\u00ebgjuar ndonj\u00ebher\u00eb!\nBurri zgjohet me kok\u00ebn e r\u00ebnduar dhe me dhimbje ther\u00ebse n\u00eb kok\u00eb pas mbr\u00ebmjes n\u00eb Fest\u00ebn e Kolektivit t\u00eb kompanis\u00eb s\u00eb tij. N\u00eb fakt, ai nuk shquhet p\u00ebr pijanec, por pijet e zakonshme kan\u00eb nj\u00eb shije krejt tjet\u00ebr nga alkooli.\nAi as nuk e kujtonte dot se si u kthye nga festa p\u00ebr n\u00eb sht\u00ebpi. Ndihej aq keq saq\u00eb, pyeste veten n\u00ebse ai kishte b\u00ebr\u00eb di\u00e7ka t\u00eb gabuar.\nSapo hodhi syt\u00eb v\u00ebrdall dhom\u00ebs, gj\u00ebja e par\u00eb q\u00eb pa ishin dy aspirina pran\u00eb nj\u00eb gote uji n\u00eb tryez\u00ebn anash krevatit. Dhe, pran\u00eb tyre, nj\u00eb tr\u00ebndafil i kuq! Ai ngrihet dhe sheh rrobat para tij, t\u00eb gjitha t\u00eb pastra dhe t\u00eb hekurosura p\u00ebr bukuri.\nAi shikon rreth dhom\u00ebs dhe sheh se \u00ebsht\u00eb e sistemuar n\u00eb m\u00ebnyr\u00eb t\u00eb p\u00ebrsosur, dhe aq past\u00ebr. Ai merr aspirinat, futet n\u00eb banjo dhe p\u00ebr habin\u00eb e tij sheh n\u00eb pasqyr\u00ebn e banjos nj\u00ebrin sy me nj\u00eb pull\u00eb t\u00eb zez\u00eb.\nPastaj atij i z\u00eb syri nj\u00eb sh\u00ebnim t\u00eb varur n\u00eb cepin e pasqyr\u00ebs t\u00eb shkruar n\u00eb t\u00eb kuqe me ca zemra n\u00eb t\u00eb dhe nj\u00eb shenj\u00eb puthje nga buz\u00ebkuqi i gruas s\u00eb tij:\n\u201cDashuria ime, m\u00ebngjesin e ke n\u00eb furr\u00eb, un\u00eb u largova her\u00ebt p\u00ebr t\u00eb bler\u00eb ushqime t\u2019i kem gati p\u00ebr t\u00eb gatuar dark\u00ebn t\u00ebnde t\u00eb preferuar sonte. T\u00eb dua dashuria ime! E jotja <3\u201d\nAi hyn n\u00eb kuzhin\u00eb dhe as q\u00eb diskutohet, n\u00eb tavolin\u00eb ka gatin m\u00ebngjesin e tij, kafeja e ngroht\u00eb vijon t\u00eb l\u00ebshoj\u00eb arom\u00ebn e saj dhe p\u00ebrbri saj, gazeta e m\u00ebngjesit.\nDjali i tij \u00ebsht\u00eb gjithashtu n\u00eb tryez\u00eb, duke ngr\u00ebn\u00eb. Ai pyet: \u201cBir\u2026 \u00c7far\u00eb ndodhi mbr\u00ebm\u00eb?\u201d\nBabi ti erdhe n\u00eb sht\u00ebpi n\u00eb ora 3 pas mesnate, i dehur dhe s\u2019kontrolloje dot as mendjen e as trupin t\u00ebnd. U rr\u00ebzove mbi tavolin\u00ebn e kafes\u00eb dhe e ke thyer at\u00eb, dhe pastaj je rr\u00ebzuar n\u00eb korridor dhe e ke marr\u00eb at\u00eb njoll\u00ebn e zez\u00eb te syri kur godite der\u00ebn.\nI hutuar, ai e pyeti t\u00eb birin, \u201cAt\u00ebher\u00eb pra, pse \u00ebsht\u00eb \u00e7do gj\u00eb \u00ebsht\u00eb m\u00ebnyr\u00eb e p\u00ebrsosur e aq e past\u00ebr? Un\u00eb kam nj\u00eb tr\u00ebndafil, dhe m\u00ebngjesi \u00ebsht\u00eb n\u00eb tryez\u00eb duke pritur p\u00ebr mua? \u201d\nDjali i tij p\u00ebrgjigjet, \u201cOh kjo\u201d! Mami ju t\u00ebrhoqi zvarr\u00eb n\u00eb dhom\u00ebn e gjumit, dhe kur ajo u p\u00ebrpoq t\u00eb t\u00eb hiqte pantallonat, ti b\u00ebrtite: \u201cL\u00ebrm\u00eb t\u00eb qet\u00eb, mos m\u00eb guxo t\u00eb m\u00eb prek\u00ebsh, jam i martuar!\u201d\nTavolina e thyer: $ 239.99\nM\u00ebngjesi i ngroht\u00eb: $ 4.20\nDy aspirina: $ 0.38.\nNj\u00eb tr\u00ebndafil: $8\nT\u00eb thuash gj\u00ebn\u00eb e duhur, n\u00eb momentin e duhur\u2026 nuk ka \u00e7mim!",
        "Mobilje p\u00ebr krijimin e dhom\u00ebs s\u00eb ndenjes t\u00eb b\u00ebra n\u00eb Itali: dollap\u00ebt an\u00ebsor, dollap\u00ebt, dollap\u00ebt prej qelqi dhe stola.\nN\u00ebse jeni duke menduar p\u00ebr mobilimine dhom\u00ebs tuaj t\u00eb ndenjes, ose po k\u00ebrkoni nj\u00eb plot\u00ebsues mobiljesh p\u00ebr projektues p\u00ebr t\u00eb mbushur nj\u00eb hap\u00ebsir\u00eb boshe, shikoni nd\u00ebr artikujt interesant dhe t\u00eb p\u00ebrsosur n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb pjes\u00eb p\u00ebr orendi elegant dhe klas. Do t\u00eb jemi t\u00eb mjaftuesh\u00ebm p\u00ebr t\u00eb kombinuar aksesor\u00ebt e duhur me dhom\u00ebn p\u00ebr ta b\u00ebr\u00eb at\u00eb m\u00eb t\u00eb mir\u00ebn n\u00eb sht\u00ebpi.\nGj\u00ebja e r\u00ebnd\u00ebsishme \u00ebsht\u00eb t\u00eb p\u00ebrpiqeni t\u00eb kombinoni stilet e ndryshme n\u00eb nj\u00eb m\u00ebnyr\u00eb harmonike duke i kushtuar v\u00ebmendje ngjyrave dhe detajeve. Kjo \u00ebsht\u00eb ajo q\u00eb do t\u00eb b\u00ebj\u00eb ndryshimin midis nj\u00eb dhome t\u00eb zakonshme dhe t\u00eb m\u00ebrzitshme n\u00eb krahasim me nj\u00eb dhom\u00eb me efekt, shum\u00eb e vler\u00ebsuar nga miqt\u00eb dhe t\u00eb af\u00ebrmit. Salla e ndenjes duhet t\u00eb jet\u00eb mikprit\u00ebse sepse \u00ebsht\u00eb pjesa e sht\u00ebpis\u00eb ku mund t\u00eb pushoni n\u00eb mbr\u00ebmje pas dark\u00ebs ose gjat\u00eb dit\u00ebs me shi.\nN\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb pjes\u00eb t\u00eb dyqanit ton\u00eb online kemi zgjedhur p\u00ebr ju shum\u00eb produkte t\u00eb ndryshme p\u00ebr q\u00ebndrimin tuaj: dollap\u00ebt e \u00e7muar t\u00eb drurit ose mdf n\u00eb stilin klasik apo modern,kabinete origjinale TV me nj\u00eb dizajn bashk\u00ebkohor dhe materiale t\u00eb reja si produkte t\u00eb b\u00ebra prej guri Vicenza dhe kristal dhe modern stola q\u00eb do t\u00eb japin nj\u00eb prekje t\u00eb cil\u00ebsis\u00eb s\u00eb mir\u00eb n\u00eb sht\u00ebpin\u00eb tuaj.\nBlerja e mobiljeve me stil klasik do t'ju jap\u00eb mund\u00ebsin\u00eb t\u00eb keni nj\u00eb efekt befasues q\u00eb dhoma juaj nuk e ka kurr\u00eb, nj\u00eb element i origjinalitetit q\u00eb thjesht e b\u00ebn at\u00eb unik. Shikoni katalogun ton\u00eb dhe zbuloni propozimet e reja t\u00eb mobiljeve p\u00ebr projektuesit. Mos hezitoni t\u00eb na kontaktoni p\u00ebr t\u00eb k\u00ebrkuar informacion, ne do t\u00eb jemi t\u00eb lumtur t'i p\u00ebrgjigjemi pyetjes tuaj dhe t'ju ndihmojm\u00eb n\u00eb blerjen e mobiljeve tuaja p\u00ebr t\u00eb krijuar nj\u00eb dhom\u00eb t\u00eb gjall\u00eb t\u00eb projektimit.",
        "N\u00eb vigjilje t\u00eb ndeshjes s\u00eb yjeve nd\u00ebrmjet ekipit t\u00eb Granit Xhak\u00ebs dhe atij t\u00eb Milot Rashic\u00ebs kan\u00eb folur edhe protagonist\u00ebt e ndeshjes.\nGranit Xhaka nd\u00ebr t\u00eb tjerash foli edhe p\u00ebr \u201cshqiponj\u00ebn\u201d e b\u00ebr\u00eb pas realizimit t\u00eb golit n\u00eb duelin me Serbin\u00eb n\u00eb Kampionatin Bot\u00ebror.\n\u201cNuk ishte nj\u00eb ndeshje e zakonshme. N\u00eb ndeshje pata shum\u00eb emocione dhe pas realizimit t\u00eb golave u hupa krejt (qeshet). Nuk ishte di\u00e7ka e planifikuar por doli e bukur. Fitorja ishte p\u00ebr Zvicr\u00ebn dhe krejt shqiptar\u00ebt\u201d, deklaroi Xhaka.\n\u201cNj\u00eb biznesmen shqiptar nga Amerika na ka paguar d\u00ebnimin, faleminderit shum\u00eb\u201d, deklaroi Xhaka.",
        "Nj\u00eb sh\u00ebtitje e mrekullueshme n\u00eb hap\u00ebsir\u00ebn ajrore p\u00ebrgjat\u00eb liqeneve t\u00eb krijuara prej akullnajave glaciale me siguri n\u00eb at\u00eb koh\u00eb, mbi natyr\u00ebn e gjelb\u00ebrt\u00eb n\u00eb t\u00eb kat\u00ebr an\u00ebt si dhe mbi ato male pitoreske q\u00eb mahnitin vizitorin dhe q\u00eb i dhurojn\u00eb nj\u00eb cop\u00ebz t\u00eb vyer n\u00eb mozaikun e veriut t\u00eb larg\u00ebt. Kjo t\u00eb duket dhe ti ndjen\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb kur ti udh\u00ebton me avion mbi teritorin e Mbret\u00ebris\u00eb suedeze./\nNga sokol DEMAKU*/\nN\u00eb Suedi ka te regjistruara sipas statistikave vendore diku mbi 95 700 liqe. Regjioni i veriut \u00ebsht\u00eb nj\u00eb nd\u00ebr m\u00eb t\u00eb pasurit me liqe diku me mbi 30 868 liqe, nd\u00ebrsa ujdhesa Gotland \u00ebsht\u00eb m\u00eb e varf\u00ebr n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb drejtim vet\u00ebm me 80 liqe.\nKjo \u00ebsht\u00eb nje statistik\u00eb q\u00eb e jep Enti Suedez SMHI (pra Enti Hidrometerorologjik Suedez)\nSuedia \u00ebsht\u00eb e bukur\u00eb dhe ta vizitosh at\u00eb n\u00eb \u00e7do centimet\u00ebr t\u00eb saj do t\u00eb thot\u00eb t\u00eb marr\u00ebsh k\u00ebnaq\u00ebsi t\u00eb pap\u00ebrshkrueshme, do ndjesh ate \u00e7ka n\u00eb t\u00eb vertet\u00eb njeriut i mungon, ajo cka njeriun e ben\u00eb t\u00eb ndjehet mir\u00eb n\u00eb \u00e7do koh\u00eb. Kjo \u00ebsht\u00eb nj\u00eb mrekulli q\u00eb nuk do e gjesh\u00eb n\u00eb asnj\u00eb kend tjet\u00ebr t\u00eb rruzullit tok\u00ebsor. Shpresojm\u00eb q\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb ndjesi do ua p\u00ebrcjellim edhe juve, sa her\u00eb q\u00eb ju sjellim n\u00eb v\u00ebmendje pjes\u00eb nga natyra dhe bukurit\u00eb e saja.\nDuke dashur t\u00eb jemi n\u00eb koherenc\u00eb t\u00eb plot\u00eb me shijet tuaja, me shijet prej lexuesi t\u00eb preferuar me at\u00eb q\u00eb do t\u00eb ishte m\u00eb e p\u00ebrshtatshme p\u00ebr t\u00eb ditur p\u00ebr k\u00ebt\u00eb vend nordik, p\u00ebr njerzit me sjellje dhe kultur\u00eb t\u00eb pa par\u00eb, me ndjenja t\u00eb qilt\u00ebrta, vend i cili n\u00eb vetvete mbart nj\u00eb k\u00ebnaq\u00ebsi t\u00eb cil\u00ebn njeiru ndjen kur gjendet k\u00ebtu e q\u00eb nuk mund ta merrni askund tjet\u00ebr.\nDuam t\u00eb themi edhe ate se njeriu ndjehet sikur \u00ebsht\u00eb \u00e7lirua nga ankthi, nga ndjenjat t\u00eb cilat i bart si nj\u00eb barr\u00eb e cila e rendon ter\u00eb jet\u00ebn, e k\u00ebtu, k\u00ebto thuase njeriu nuk i ndjen, e mendojm se \u00ebsht\u00eb ambienti njerzor i cili \u00ebsht\u00eb krijuar nga pasardh\u00ebsit e Viking\u00ebve t\u00eb lasht\u00eb, t\u00eb cil\u00ebt njer\u00ebz jan\u00eb mik\u00ebprit\u00ebs, zem\u00ebrgjer\u00eb, me ambicje pozitive p\u00ebr jet\u00ebn, njer\u00ebz q\u00eb kur ti do i takosh do mendosh se tek k\u00ebta nuk egziston shprehja \u201cJo\u201d dhe se k\u00ebta jan\u00eb ata t\u00eb cil\u00ebt \u00e7do her\u00eb dhe n\u00eb \u00e7do koh\u00eb mendojn\u00eb p\u00ebr vet\u00ebn dhe t\u00eb ardhmen e tyre.\nZhvillimi demokratik dhe ekonomia e vendit ka qen\u00eb dhe \u00ebsht\u00eb synimi kryesor i k\u00ebtyre njer\u00ebzve t\u00eb thejsht\u00eb dhe zemergj\u00ebr\u00eb, njer\u00ebz t\u00eb cil\u00ebt edhe k\u00ebta kan\u00eb pasur baticat dhe zbaticat\u00eb e tyre n\u00eb jet\u00eb. Edhe suedz\u00ebt sikur edhe ne shqiptar\u00ebt sot, ata dikur ishin ata t\u00eb cil\u00ebt m\u00ebrguan me t\u00eb madhe, iknin nga veriu, iknin nga trojet e tyre sepse nuk kishin mund\u00ebsi ta siguronin egzistenc\u00ebn e tyre, por ne jo q\u00eb ikem nga kjo por edhe trysnit dhe zullumet na e b\u00ebn\u00eb jet\u00ebn t\u00eb padurueshme. E si duket k\u00ebta njer\u00ebz ne na kan\u00eb kuptua m\u00eb s\u00eb miri dhe kan\u00eb hapur zemr\u00ebn dhe na kan\u00eb pritur\u00eb dhe ndihmuar q\u00eb t\u00eb jem pjes\u00eb e k\u00ebtij vendi t\u00eb mrekulluesh\u00ebm.\nAjo q\u00eb do t\u2019ju ofrojm\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb her\u00eb, \u00ebsht\u00eb nj\u00eb sh\u00ebtitje e mrekullueshme n\u00eb disa pjes\u00eb t\u00eb k\u00ebtij vendi e q\u00eb p\u00ebrve\u00e7 se na japin nj\u00eb pasqyr\u00eb t\u00eb jet\u00ebs s\u00eb njer\u00ebzve k\u00ebtu, ne do kemi rastin t\u00eb njihemi edhe me jet\u00ebn, kultur\u00ebn dhe tradit\u00ebn e tyre. \u00casht\u00eb inetersant t\u00eb fillojm\u00eb me krahin\u00ebn Sm\u00e5land, e cila \u00ebsht\u00eb nj\u00eb krahin\u00eb n\u00eb jug lindje t\u00eb Suedis\u00eb e \u00ebsht\u00eb shum\u00eb interesant n\u00eb fillim t\u00eb dim di\u00e7 m\u00eb tep\u00ebr p\u00ebr k\u00ebt\u00eb krahin\u00eb e n\u00eb baz\u00eb t\u00eb disa te dhenave del se diku nga viti 500 para Krish. ka qen\u00eb k\u00ebnet\u00eb dhe liqe e pasur me hekur. Por n\u00eb baz\u00eb te t\u00eb dh\u00ebnave q\u00eb njeriu mund t\u00eb gjej\u00eb del se nga mesi i viteve 1800 hyri n\u00eb p\u00ebrdorim industria e p\u00ebrpunimit t\u00eb drurit dhe xhamit, uzinat metalurgjike, k\u00ebshtu q\u00eb edhe jeta k\u00ebtu ka ndryshua. K\u00ebt\u00eb koh\u00eb do kemi nj\u00eb rritje t\u00eb madhe t\u00eb popullsis\u00eb dhe n\u00eb nj\u00eb an\u00eb do kemi edhe uri dhe varf\u00ebri n\u00eb rrethe, e nga mesi i viteve 1800 shum\u00eb t\u00eb rinj kan\u00eb emigruar n\u00eb Amerik\u00eb shaku i varf\u00ebris\u00eb. K\u00ebt\u00eb period\u00eb t\u00eb v\u00ebshtir\u00eb t\u00eb jet\u00ebs p\u00ebr shum\u00eb familje suedeze dhe suedez shum\u00eb shkrimtar dhe poet suedez e kan\u00eb pasyqruar n\u00eb shkrimet dhe veprat e tyre.\nVijon(Pjes\u00eb n\u00eb vazhdime nga libri n\u00eb dor\u00ebshkrim\u201d Nj\u00eb udh\u00ebtim magjeps n\u00eb veriun e larg\u00ebt\u201di autor\u00ebve: Rovena Vata dhe Sokol Demaku)",
        "Apple ka l\u00ebshuar p\u00ebr t\u00eb gjith\u00eb iOS 14, q\u00eb p\u00ebrb\u00ebn versionin m\u00eb t\u00eb ri t\u00eb sistemit t\u00eb saj operativ p\u00ebr iPhone.\niOS 14, i prezantuar muaj m\u00eb par\u00eb, sjell disa risi. Widget me nj\u00eb dizajn t\u00eb ri n\u00eb Home Screen, App Library, nj\u00eb m\u00ebnyr\u00eb t\u00eb re p\u00ebr t\u2019u qasur n\u00eb App Store me App Clips, funksione t\u00eb reja p\u00ebr mesazhet dhe shum\u00eb risi t\u00eb tjera q\u00eb do t\u2019i p\u00ebrmendim n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb artikull t\u00eb detajuar.\nTani Widgets shfaqin informacione t\u00eb domosdoshme me nj\u00eb v\u00ebshtrim dhe mund t\u2019i fiksoni, me p\u00ebrmasat q\u00eb d\u00ebshironi, n\u00eb Home Screen. \u00c7do p\u00ebrdorues mund t\u00eb krijoj\u00eb nj\u00eb Stack me widget, q\u00eb shfryt\u00ebzon inteligjenc\u00ebn e integruar n\u00eb iPhone p\u00ebr t\u00eb shfaqur nj\u00eb widget t\u00eb caktuar n\u00eb baz\u00eb t\u00eb or\u00ebs, vendit dhe aktivitetit.\nFaqet e Home Screen mund t\u00eb shfaqein widget t\u00eb p\u00ebrsonalizuar p\u00ebr pun\u00eb, udh\u00ebtime, sport, koh\u00ebn e lir\u00eb dhe interese t\u00eb tjera. N\u00eb fund t\u00eb faqes do t\u00eb gjeni App Library, nj\u00eb hap\u00ebsir\u00eb t\u00eb re q\u00eb organizon automatikisht t\u00eb gjitha aplikacionet, duke vendosur t\u00eb shfaq vet\u00ebm ato q\u00eb jan\u00eb m\u00eb t\u00eb domosdoshme p\u00ebr p\u00ebrdoruesin n\u00eb at\u00eb moment. Mund t\u00eb vendosni sa faqe t\u00eb Home Screen d\u00ebshironi t\u00eb shfaqni, ose t\u00eb fshehni.\nTelefonatat tradicionale dhe FaceTime tani kan\u00eb nj\u00eb dizajn t\u00eb ri m\u00eb kompakt q\u00eb b\u00ebn t\u00eb mundur q\u00eb p\u00ebrdoruesi t\u00eb mos humbas\u00eb at\u00eb \u00e7far\u00eb po b\u00ebnte p\u00ebrpara se t\u00eb merrte nj\u00eb telefonat\u00eb. Me funksionin Picture-in-Picture, p\u00ebrdoruesit e iPhone mund t\u00eb shikojn\u00eb nj\u00eb video ose t\u2019i p\u00ebrgjigjen nj\u00eb telefonate FaceTime nd\u00ebrkoh\u00eb q\u00eb vazhdojn\u00eb t\u00eb p\u00ebrdorin nj\u00eb aplikacion tjet\u00ebr.\nApp Clips jan\u00eb t\u00eb lidhura me nj\u00eb produkt t\u00eb caktuar ose biznes, dhe ngarkohen n\u00eb vet\u00ebm pak sekonda duke e ndihmuar p\u00ebrdoruesin t\u00eb kryej\u00eb nj\u00eb aktivitet specifik, p\u00ebr shembull t\u00eb paguaj\u00eb nj\u00eb kafe apo nj\u00eb parking. Jan\u00eb t\u00eb thjeshta p\u00ebr t\u2019u zbuluar, mjafton t\u00eb skansiononi nj\u00eb kod t\u00eb ri App Clip t\u00eb krijuar nga Apple ose n\u00ebp\u00ebrmjet tag NFC dhe kodin QR.\nMe aplikacionin e ri Messages tani \u00ebsht\u00eb m\u00eb e thjesht\u00eb t\u00eb q\u00ebndroni n\u00eb kontakt. P\u00ebrdoruesit mund t\u00eb vendosin t\u00eb fiksojn\u00eb nj\u00eb bashk\u00ebbisedim lart n\u00eb list\u00ebn e mesazheve dhe t\u00eb personalizojn\u00eb bisedat duke vendosur nj\u00eb foto grupi ose nj\u00eb emoji.\nMaps ka shtuar disa udh\u00ebzime t\u00eb reja p\u00ebr \u00e7iklitat, itinerare p\u00ebr automejtet elektrike dhe guda t\u00eb detajuara p\u00ebr qytetet. \u00cbsht\u00eb shtuar aplikacioni i ri Translate p\u00ebr t\u00eb p\u00ebrkthyer bisedat, e disponueshme n\u00eb 11 gjuh\u00eb.\nSiri ka zgjeruar njohurit\u00eb e saj, tani na ndihmon t\u00eb gjejm\u00eb p\u00ebrgjigjet n\u00eb internet dhe mund t\u00eb d\u00ebrgoj\u00eb edhe mesazhe audio. Tani fal\u00eb \u00c7el\u00ebsave dixhital, p\u00ebrdoruesit mund t\u00eb p\u00ebrdorin nj\u00eb iPhone p\u00ebr t\u00eb hapur nj\u00eb automjet.",
        "Pas takimit q\u00eb zhvilloi me liderin demokrat, Spahiu pohoi p\u00ebr mediat se deri m\u00eb tani nuk \u00ebsht\u00eb r\u00ebn\u00eb dakord p\u00ebr listat e kandidat\u00ebve p\u00ebr zgjedhjet e 25 qershorit.\nAi l\u00ebshoi nd\u00ebr t\u00eb tjera dhe nj\u00eb deklarat\u00eb, nd\u00ebrsa tha se largohet nga politika n\u00ebse nuk p\u00ebrfaq\u00ebsohet n\u00eb zgjedhje.\n\u201cKa nj\u00eb or\u00eb koh\u00eb q\u00eb t\u00eb na kthej\u00eb p\u00ebrgjigje.\nSakrifikuam partit\u00eb p\u00ebr t\u00eb dhe na preu n\u00eb bes\u00eb.\nLargohem nga politika n\u00ebse nuk p\u00ebrfaq\u00ebsohem n\u00eb listat e PD\u201d, tha Spahiu.\n\u201cKemi qen\u00eb n\u00eb nj\u00eb betej\u00eb ku kishim tre marr\u00ebveshje. E para ishte ajo e Republik\u00ebs s\u00eb Re duke p\u00ebrmbysur Edi Ram\u00ebn si kryeminist\u00ebr. E dyta erdhi si pasoj\u00eb e nj\u00eb kriz\u00eb t\u00eb r\u00ebnd\u00eb mes Bash\u00ebs dhe Ram\u00ebs, e cila i hoqi mund\u00ebsin\u00eb partive p\u00ebr t\u2019u regjistruar n\u00eb zgjedhje.\nDhe kemi nj\u00eb marr\u00ebveshje t\u00eb tret\u00eb q\u00eb ne si parti opozitare firmos\u00ebm t\u00eb mos regjistrohemi n\u00eb KQZ n\u00ebn premtimin e Bash\u00ebs se do t\u00eb p\u00ebrfaq\u00ebsohemi n\u00eb listat e PD.\nPra duke ndjekur nj\u00eb taktik\u00eb elektorale, duke u grupuar n\u00ebn logon e Partis\u00eb Demokratike. Q\u00eb nga ajo dit\u00eb, un\u00eb nuk e kam konsideruar si Pazar t\u00eb gj\u00ebse s\u00eb gjall\u00eb list\u00ebn sepse kam qen\u00eb n\u00ebn garancin\u00eb i cili lidhi bes\u00ebn me kuqezinjt\u00eb n\u00eb \u00e7ad\u00ebr p\u00ebr 90 dit\u00eb.\nJu keni qen\u00eb d\u00ebshmitar\u00eb q\u00eb kuqezinjt\u00eb ishin boshti i kauz\u00ebs.\nPor edhe n\u00eb bes\u00eblidhjen e zotit Basha q\u00eb t\u00eb gjith\u00eb ne do p\u00ebrfshiheshim n\u00eb lista sepse po vet\u00ebsakrifikoheshim.\nKam pasur nj\u00eb bised\u00eb me liderin e PD p\u00ebr t\u00eb cil\u00ebn nuk kemi r\u00ebn\u00eb dakord. Kemi parashtruar disa parime t\u00eb cilat un\u00eb nuk mund t\u2019i tradhtoj p\u00ebrball\u00eb njer\u00ebzve q\u00eb m\u00eb kan\u00eb ndjekur p\u00ebr 6 vite n\u00eb protestat kund\u00ebr PS dhe PD.\nKemi r\u00ebn\u00eb dakord q\u00eb pretendimet e Aleanc\u00ebs Kuqezi, Basha ti konsultoj\u00eb me koleg\u00ebt e tij dhe ne k\u00ebt\u00eb situat\u00eb t\u00eb v\u00ebshtir\u00eb ta kap\u00ebrcejm\u00eb dhe PD ta diskutoj\u00eb brenda 60 minutash me kryesin\u00eb.\nPo kalojm\u00eb nj\u00eb situat\u00eb t\u00eb v\u00ebshtir\u00eb sepse un\u00eb futa qindra aktivist\u00eb n\u00ebn bes\u00ebn e Bash\u00ebs se n\u00eb luft\u00eb do t\u00eb shkonim s\u00ebbashku dhe do t\u00eb ishim t\u00eb pandar\u00eb.\nMbetem i mendimit se n\u00eb k\u00ebto 60 minuta do t\u00eb reflektohet. P\u00ebrndryshe do jap dor\u00ebheqjen dhe do t\u00ebrhiqem nga politika\u201d, tha ai.\nPor Basha i ktheu p\u00ebrgjigjie."
